# Hero / Service / About Rebuild + AnimatedProjects Effect

Rebuild Professional mode's editorial sections per the `hero-service-about-spec.md` and adapt the AnimatedProjects scroll effect — all using real content, `motion/react`, and the existing design-token system.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Stat card numbers** — The existing `professionalAchievements` data uses real-ish counts (7 projects, 8 certifications, 4 internships). These are derived from the content data and reasonable, but please confirm whether these are the final numbers you want displayed, or if you'd like different metrics (e.g., hackathons, papers, GitHub repos). The spec warned against fabricating numbers.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Phone number visibility** — `shared.ts` includes `tel:+919730100346`. The spec flags publishing a personal number on a public page. This plan **excludes the phone card** from the rebuilt About section. Say the word if you want it included.

> [!WARNING]
> **Social links** — Only GitHub and LinkedIn have real URLs in `shared.ts`. Instagram is empty, and there's no Behance/Dribbble. The About section will only show GitHub + LinkedIn + Email. If you have other real profiles, provide the URLs.

