### Shared UI — CountUpStat

#### [NEW] [CountUpStat.tsx](file:///d:/Resume/Portfolio/MyPortfolioDev/sia-portfolio/components/professional/CountUpStat.tsx)

One reusable count-up stat card (spec: "build one `<CountUpStat />`, not three bespoke copies"):
- Uses `motion/react`'s `useInView` to trigger
- `useMotionValue` + `animate()` tween from 0 → end value over ~1.2s ease-out
- Renders the number + suffix + label
- Accepts `value: number`, `suffix?: string`, `label: string`
- SSR-safe: renders the final number server-side, count-up is client-only decoration

