## Decisions Made

| Decision | Choice | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| "My Story" button | In-page anchor `#timeline` | Content already on the page; a separate `/about` route would duplicate it |
| Phone number | **Excluded** | Spec flags it as optional; email + LinkedIn suffice |
| Social icons | GitHub + LinkedIn only | Only ones with real URLs in `shared.ts` |
| Stat card numbers | 7 projects / 8 certs / 4 internships | Derived from actual content data — **flagged for confirmation** |
| Skills + Timeline placement | After About, before Footer | Natural reading order; "My Story" CTA anchors to Timeline |
| `"View all projects"` link | Kept, anchors to `#projects-all` | Links to the remaining non-featured projects shown below |
| `↗ LaunchNow` watermark | **Removed** | Template branding, not Kirtiraj's |

